      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis power-law model form and turbulence closure must be assessed for suitability in the VAD operating regime with documented model-form uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty not assessed. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is used without formal assessment of model-form error or comparison to alternative model forms. Epistemic gap flagged at MRL 5."
